            }}>{`Organize a Meetup`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "../meetups/README.md"
            }}>{`Improve Meetup Guides`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "../makerdao-mcd-faqs/README.md"
            }}>{`Add or Update to MakerDAO FAQs`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "../translations/README.md"
            }}>{`Translate MakerDAO Resources`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "./gnr-summary-guide.md"
            }}>{`Write Risk & Governance Meeting Summaries`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "https://github.com/makerdao/awesome-makerdao"
            }}>{`Curate Awesome-MakerDAO`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "https://github.com/makerdao/community/projects/2?card_filter_query=label%3A%22help+wanted%22"
            }}>{`Explore open bounties with Help-Wanted label`}</a>{` or `}<a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "https://forum.makerdao.com/c/comm-dev/help-wanted/11"
            }}>{`Browse Help-Wanted section of the MakerDAO Forum`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "./contributor-onboarding-guide.md"
            }}>{`Propose initiatives with a Community Development Initiative Proposal (CDIP)`}</a></li>
          <li parentName="ul"><a parentName="li" {...{
              "href": "../grants/README.md"
            }}>{`Apply for a Development Grant for a Large Project`}</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Signal interest to the particular opportunity as a comment on the Forum Post, Github Issue, or `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://chat.makerdao.com/channel/community-development"
        }}>{`#community-development chat channel.`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`If a contribution does not fall within these scopes, discuss personal interests and relevant skills to the Contributing Team to help determine a well-suited project.`}</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>{`Approve`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Most contributions require some form of approval before compensated work can be started. A good first step is to connect with an Advisor, Lead, or Approver in the `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://chat.makerdao.com/channel/community-development"
        }}>{`#community-development chat channel.`}</a></li>
    </ul>
    <h3>{`Work`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Follow best practices that can be found in the `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "./contributor-onboarding-guide.md"
        }}>{`Contributor Onboarding Guide.`}</a></li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Define and talk to stakeholders early on.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Communicate work in progress, blockers, and other updates regularly.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Don’t hesitate to ask for help for feedback in the `}<a parentName="li" {...{
          "href": "https://chat.makerdao.com/channel/community-development"
        }}>{`#community-development chat Channel.`}</a></li>
    </ul>
    <h3>{`Complete`}</h3>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`A contribution is paid out when a milestone or a project is complete and goes through a final approval by the Approver.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Ask an Advisor or Approver for instructions on submitting a payment request.`}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>{`For further questions or insights, talk with the team in the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://chat.makerdao.com/channel/community-development"
      }}>{`#community-development chat channel.`}</a></p>

    </MDXLayout>;
